If the repr of the dict is important for you you can just create a custom dict class and override it.

for example:

    class CustomDict(dict):
       def __repr__(self):
           items = &#39;&#39;
           item = &#39;{key}: {value},\n&#39;
           full_repr = &#39;{{\n{items}}}&#39;
           for key, value in self.items():
               items += item.format(key=key.__repr__(), value=value.__repr__())
